doc.after: Philippine culture is a combination of Eastern and Western cultures The Philippines exhibits aspects found in other Asian countries with a Malay 378 heritage yet its culture also displays a significant amount of Spanish and American influences Traditional festivities known as barrio fiestas district festivals to commemorate the feast days of patron saints are common
